snippet.title: Sonic Dungeons: Prototype FPS (SAGE 2024 Trailer)
snippet.description:
Trailer for Sonic Dungeons: Prototype. A concept for a Sonic fan-game set in the Archie Sonic universe. Take control of the Freedom Fighters to defeat the dark forces of Dr. Eggman in this first-person action game. 

Release Date: September 6th, 2024
LinkTree: https://linktr.ee/dungeonsanddels

Trailer Music: 
"Battle On!" (Instrumental) by Andrew and Mark Twining 
Little Battlers eXperience English Dub
